<% content_for(:heading) do %>
  <%= @page_title %>
<% end %>

<%= render 'meta/meta_sidebar' %>
<div class="reading-width">
  <p>
    Parliamentary Search contains a built-in feature to help our team debug the application. This includes information
    about what was actually searched for and links to source systems.
  </p>

  <p>
    Librarian tools are available from both search result pages and object pages.
  </p>

  <p>
    To access librarian tools, users on a Windows PC need to press:
  </p>

  <p>
    <code>
      Ctrl, Alt + D
    </code>
  </p>

  <p>
    Mac users need to press:
  </p>

  <p>
    <code>
      Control, Option + D
    </code>
  </p>

  <p>
    Not all the links shown by librarian tools will work for all users. The link to Solr will only work for users on the
    parliamentary network with a subscription key. The Indexing link will only work for users on the parliamentary
    network with access to the Indexing Tool.
  </p>
</div>